comment: Wow, Delphine's hell is seeing her children in pain. Marie's hell is torturing people, being unable to stop. This show is brilliant
Delphine's hell is seeing her children in pain. Marie's is that she realises she didn't want to hurt them or make them suffer anymore...but she can't stop.
It's interesting how hell is psychological rather than physical.
It was an interesting idea how they portrayed hell as every ones worst fears and regrets.
